The drawing shows in:
Fig. 1: an overview of a cabin of an aircraft integrating RFID-devices according to a first embodiment of a fuselage;
Fig 2: a simplified scheme of a configuration and monitoring system for cabin elements, aircraft components and supply items of a cabin and fuselage of an aircraft according to a second embodiment;
Fig. 3: a simplified scheme of the configuration and monitoring system for cabin elements, integrating sensor units in the RFID-devices according to a third embodiment;
Fig. 4: a detailed picture of the overhead panel integrating a repeater according to a forth embodiment;
Fig. 5: a simplified scheme for exemplifying a concept of integrating RFID-devices in a passenger seat according to a fifth embodiment.
